	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Making a snes cart...The cart has 8k ram on it, but the game requires 32k ram....everything else matches up that is required.  Could I just switch that 8k ram chip out with a 32k ram chip, would that work, or would there be more required than that?  Thanks!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
